 working code for web service api. Any help will be appreciated. Thanks in advance.</p>  <p>==== EDIT====</p>  <p>Mention : it is server url.</p>  <p>I figured out one more thing. If I run this code in ios 8 and above device it is working fine. And this problem is occurred in ios 7 device. I'm dealing with iPod with ios7. I have checked in ios8 devices like iPhone and iPad, it is working fine.</p>